WEBVTT

1
00:00:00.001 --> 00:00:01.453
Guilty is that witch

2
00:00:03.857 --> 00:00:05.604
who has seduced a monk

3
00:00:07.215 --> 00:00:10.971
and has practiced her diabolical ritual within this hallowed place.

4
00:00:14.081 --> 00:00:15.450
Guilty is Salvatore

5
00:00:17.652 --> 00:00:19.586
who has confessed to his heretical past

6
00:00:20.129 --> 00:00:22.579
and was caught in flagrante delicto with a witch!

7
00:00:23.732 --> 00:00:27.009
Guilty is Remigio de Varagine

8
00:00:28.409 --> 00:00:31.599
who, in addition to being unrepentant of his heresies

9
00:00:31.690 --> 00:00:34.858
was caught attempting to escape after murdering Severinus.

10
00:00:35.216 --> 00:00:36.324
That's a lie!

11
00:00:36.817 --> 00:00:40.108
I never killed the herbalist or anyone else in this abbey!

12
00:00:40.463 --> 00:00:42.257
I therefore request you

13
00:00:43.170 --> 00:00:45.545
to confirm my sentence, my lord abbot.

14
00:00:51.696 --> 00:00:54.462
My heart is filled with sorrow

15
00:00:56.253 --> 00:00:58.676
but I can find no reason to contest

16
00:00:59.603 --> 00:01:02.500
the just sentence of the Holy Inquisition.

17
00:01:05.086 --> 00:01:06.818
And you, William of Baskerville?

18
00:01:15.136 --> 00:01:15.689
Yes.

19
00:01:17.033 --> 00:01:17.807
He is guilty.

20
00:01:19.280 --> 00:01:21.568
Guilty of having, in his youth

21
00:01:22.325 --> 00:01:24.619
misinterpreted the message of the gospels.

22
00:01:26.859 --> 00:01:30.563
And he is guilty of having confused

23
00:01:31.210 --> 00:01:36.329
the love of poverty with the blind destruction of wealth and property.

24
00:01:39.056 --> 00:01:43.493
But, my lord abbot, he is innocent of the crimes

25
00:01:43.773 --> 00:01:45.861
that have bathed your abbey in blood.

26
00:01:48.527 --> 00:01:51.726
For Brother Remigio cannot read Greek.

27
00:01:52.586 --> 00:01:54.274
And this entire mystery

28
00:01:54.868 --> 00:01:58.758
hinges on the theft and possession of a book written in Greek

29
00:01:58.910 --> 00:02:01.395
and hidden in some secret part of the library.

30
00:02:02.787 --> 00:02:06.368
Since the verdict of the Inquisition has been disputed by brother William

31
00:02:06.393 --> 00:02:09.800
we are obliged to extract the prisoner's confession to murder.

32
00:02:10.180 --> 00:02:12.177
Take him to the forge and show him the instruments.

33
00:02:14.549 --> 00:02:16.482
I'll confess anything you want

34
00:02:17.969 --> 00:02:19.679
but don't torture me.

35
00:02:20.319 --> 00:02:22.885
I can't live through it, not like Salvatore.

36
00:02:23.052 --> 00:02:23.792
Very well.

37
00:02:25.131 --> 00:02:26.018
Why did you kill them?

38
00:02:28.146 --> 00:02:28.946
Why?

39
00:02:30.046 --> 00:02:32.696
I don't know why.

40
00:02:35.382 --> 00:02:38.157
- Because you were inspired by the devil? - Yes.

41
00:02:39.138 --> 00:02:42.297
That's it. I was inspired by the devil.

42
00:02:42.784 --> 00:02:47.503
I am inspired by the devil!

43
00:02:48.038 --> 00:02:52.771
Adrammelech, Lucifer, I summon you, lords of hell!

44
00:02:53.155 --> 00:02:54.509
Alastor!

45
00:02:56.052 --> 00:02:57.031
Azazel!

46
00:02:59.212 --> 00:03:01.229
The shepherd has done his duty

47
00:03:02.132 --> 00:03:05.579
and the infected sheep must now be consigned to the purifying flame.

48
00:03:06.992 --> 00:03:08.941
You may burn Brother Remigio

49
00:03:09.654 --> 00:03:13.158
but you will not stop the crimes being committed in this abbey.

50
00:03:14.139 --> 00:03:16.052
Other monks will meet their deaths here

51
00:03:16.766 --> 00:03:19.120
and they also will have blackened fingers

52
00:03:19.700 --> 00:03:21.088
and blackened tongues!

